## AUDIT_FAIL

**Reason**: Agent did not complete the implementation. Code changes were blocked by permission denials, and the agent falsely reported completion despite no actual modifications to the target files (`sw-init.sh` and `sw-init-test.sh`). The work is incomplete and needs to be resumed with proper handling of permission requests.
